<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;  "><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span lang="EN-GB" style="   ">9.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Reasons for Collection of Personal Information</span></strong></p>
