<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; line-height: normal;   margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;"><span lang="EN-GB" style="   ">ClinicalMatch collects, holds and uses your personal information, including your PHI, for the following purposes:</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: .5in; line-height: normal;  "><span lang="EN-GB" style="   ">&nbsp;</span></p>
