<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: -.5in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l11 level1 lfo1;   margin: 0in 0in .0001pt 1.0in;"><span lang="EN-GB" style="  font-family: 'Noto Sans Symbols'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Noto Sans Symbols'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Noto Sans Symbols';  "><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">✔<span style=" ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span lang="EN-GB" style="   ">to enable you to fully access and use the Website;</span></p>
