<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -.5in; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span lang="EN-GB">10.<span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Changes to This Privacy Practices Notice</span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -.5in; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -.5in; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span lang="EN-GB"><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></strong><span lang="EN-GB" style="  ">ClinicalMatch reserves the right to change the contents of this notice and any such changes will be effective with reference to any and all information ClinicalMatch already has on you and any information that will be received in future. Any changes will be posted on the Website and you may request a copy of the current Privacy Practices Notice.</span></p>
