<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;"><span lang="EN-GB" style="  ">In the event of any dispute between ClinicalMatch and the Registered User, both parties hereby expressly and irrevocably agree that such dispute shall be settled exclusively by way of arbitration.</span></p>
