<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;"><span lang="EN-GB" style="  ">The basis of the arbitration shall be based on the laws and regulations relating to arbitration that shall be effective from time to time in the State of Delaware unless agreed to in writing otherwise by ClinicalMatch and the Registered User and it is expressly agreed that the arbitration laws and regulations in any and all other jurisdictions is/are expressly excluded.</span></p>
