<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;"><span lang="EN-GB" style="  ">In any event, the Registered User shall not be at liberty to raise any dispute in respect of any order until the lapse of thirty (30) clear days from the placement of the order.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;"><span lang="EN-GB" style="  ">&nbsp;</span></p>
