<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: -.5in; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span lang="EN-GB" style="  ">27.  <span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp; </span>Disclosure of The Registered User&rsquo;s Personal Information</span></strong></p>
