<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;"><span lang="EN-GB" style="  ">In the event that ClinicalMatch and/or its assets, including but not limited to, the Service,<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>and the Website and all intellectual property relating thereto, are purchased by a third party, in whole or in part, ClinicalMatch shall at all times retain the right to transfer the personal details of the Registered User and all information relating to and/or provided by the Registered User to the Buyer.</span></p>
