<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;"><span lang="EN-GB" style="  ">Notwithstanding any contrary provisions or terms set out in this TOU, the entire content of this TOU is only for the benefit of ClinicalMatch and the Registered User and their respective successors and assigns and this TOU does not in any way whatsoever create or bestow any rights and/or benefits in favour of any third party.</span></p>
