<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;"><span lang="EN-GB" style="  ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;"><a name="_heading=h.gjdgxs"></a><span lang="EN-GB" style="  ">The Registered User may submit a request in writing at any time to for private information to be removed from ClinicalMatch&rsquo;s database. ClinicalMatch shall process such written notification from the Registered User within thirty (30) clear days from the receipt of such notice provided always that all Order IDs and any personal details attached thereto will not under any circumstances be deleted, removed and/or amended in any way whatsoever. Your written request should be by way of an email directed to </span><span lang="EN-GB"><a href="mailto:customersupport@starzly.net"><span style="   color: #0563c1;">support@</span></a></span><u><span lang="EN-GB" style="   color: #0563c1;">clinicalmatch</span></u><span lang="EN-GB" style="  ">.com. Your email should give details of the private information you wish to have removed.</span></p>
