<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;"><span lang="EN-GB" style="  ">ClinicalMatch collects information about visitors to the Website through the use of Cookies. For information on ClinicalMatch&rsquo; policies relating to the use of cookie, please visit our Privacy Policy page.</span></p>
